{"article_id":"9MiveUeeneUcsmhz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The nine justices on the Supreme Court gave no clear indication on Monday","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"of how they might rule in a potentially significant case","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"regarding free speech on the Internet .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Anthony Elonis was convicted of making threats of violence","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"and sentenced to nearly four years in prison","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"after posting hostile messages on Facebook about his community and his then-estranged wife ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"after she obtained a protective order against him .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Elonis claims","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"his threats were n't serious","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"and that he was merely posting original rap lyrics .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"The conviction was a violation of his First Amendment right to freedom of speech ,","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"his lawyers argue .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"The case is the first major test of free speech rights on the Internet ,","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"but the court 's eventual ruling could apply to more traditional forms of communication .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"correspondent Jan Crawford reports","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"after hearing complicated and convoluted arguments from both Elonis ' lawyers and government lawyers ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"the justices seemed skeptical of both sides .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"`` The justices were all over the place","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"because this is a really complex issue , ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Crawford reported after the arguments .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"`` No one could tell you after this argument how the court is going to decide this case","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"because I do n't think","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"the justices know . ''","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"John Elwood , an attorney for Elonis , said after the arguments","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"that he thought","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"they went `` reasonably well ''","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"but agreed","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"the outcome would be `` very hard to tell . ''","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"that a victory for the government in this case could have far-reaching consequences for communications online ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"where the intent of one 's message is not always clear .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"A sketch from the Supreme Court on Dec. 1 , 2014 , during arguments in Elonis v. United States , a case about free speech rights online .","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"AP","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"`` Increasingly people","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"who speak on the Internet ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"which is where much speech happens today ...","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"could be held subject to felony liability","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"not because they intended to ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"you know ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"threaten anybody","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"but because somebody misinterpreted their comments as a threat , ''","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Elwood said .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"`` That is a risk on the Internet ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"where you 're frequently speaking to people ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"you know ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"without the context of tone of voice , body gestures , and frequently talking to people","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"who you do n't even know in the physical world . ''","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Jeff Dion , deputy executive director of the National Center for Victims of Crime , said after Monday 's arguments","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"that the government made a strong case .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Throwing out Elonis ' conviction would effectively `` make a rulebook","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"on how to legally threaten your spouse , ''","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Dion argued .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Justice Samuel Alito indicated","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"he agreed with that point ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"according to Scotusblog .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Should Elonis win ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"it would invalidate a majority of stalking statutes in the U.S. ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Dion said .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"If `` there is a requirement","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"that the defendant actually intended to place the victim in fear ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"it could become much more difficult for the government ever to get a conviction for stalking , ''","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Stalking is a precursor crime","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"which often leads to sexual assault and homicide ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"he pointed out .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"The majority of women","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"who were murdered by current or former intimate partners","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"were stalked in the 12 months","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"preceding their death .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Paulette Sullivan Moore of the National Network to End Domestic Violence added","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"that `` a threat is a threat , ''","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"whether it comes via social media or otherwise .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"`` If I leave the message on your windshield ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"or post it on your door ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"or post it on the Internet","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"-- however I communicate ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"whatever medium","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"I use","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"to communicate the threat --","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"does n't make it any less a threat , ''","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"According to Scotusblog ,","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"`` The Justices did not spend a lot of time","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"analyzing","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"whether the Internet was different from other forums of communications ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"[ although ] now and then a Justice would throw in a presumably knowing reference to Eminem or to rappers more generally . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":173,"left":89,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":0,"right":88,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":117,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":97,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":95,"right":96,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":92,"right":94,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":90,"right":91,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":91,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":7,"right":93,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":98,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":115,"left":112,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":107,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":101,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":14,"right":100,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":15,"right":99,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"c